rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Seems like that Ivan guy was
sneaking snacks in the storehouse
again.

rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Kaleena caught him and treated him
like a felon. It turned into a huge fuss.

rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I managed to calm it down, but it made
me realize how different the values
are between Superbia and Iira.

rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Ivan can never control his appetite.
What he did was wrong, but he didn't
really mean any major harm...

rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm going to talk to Kaleena again.
That might help clear things up! I want
to learn more about Superbia, too.

rows.label: tlk70000053_03_msg0006
rows.name:
To understand another person, you first
have to accept the differences between
you. Adel-sama taught me that.
